data.description: Welcome to your hidden gem within the sought-after Seascape Resort! Nestled behind its exclusive gates lies this delightful villa, meticulously maintained. This unit is ideally situated in the highly desirable Tennis Village of Seascape.Step outside, and you'll find yourself just a stone's throw away from the tennis courts and the only heated pool among the four available in the complex. Additional amenities include pickleball courts, and a short 7-minute stroll will take you to the Seascape Deeded beach, complete with dedicated beach parking and the renowned Whales Tail Restaurant/Bar. Vacationers adore Tennis Village, as it offers covered parking and expansive enclosed outdoor patios, a rare and coveted feature in any Destin resort condo.
